# Combat Stances

At the start of every fight, you make a fundamental decision: how will you approach this conflict? Your stance represents your combat philosophy—whether you press forward aggressively, hold back defensively, or adapt moment by moment to changing circumstances.

Stances aren't just flavor. They determine when you act in the turn order, how you generate Momentum, what bonuses and penalties you face, and what special capabilities you can access. Mastering all three stances and knowing when to switch between them is the mark of a skilled combatant.

